sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User
    participant Kong as Kong Gateway
    participant Purchase as Purchase Orchestrator
    participant SeatInv as Seat Inventory (gRPC)
    participant Rabbit as RabbitMQ
    participant OutSys as OutSystems Credit API
    participant Ticket as Ticket Service
    participant Ledger as Credit Transaction Service

    User->>Kong: POST /purchase/hold/{inventoryId}
    Kong->>Purchase: Forward JWT + apikey request
    Purchase->>SeatInv: HoldSeat(inventoryId, userId, 300s)
    SeatInv-->>Purchase: held + holdToken + heldUntil
    Purchase->>Rabbit: publish seat_hold_ttl_queue message
    Purchase-->>User: 200 hold created

    User->>Kong: POST /purchase/confirm/{inventoryId}
    Kong->>Purchase: eventId + holdToken
    Purchase->>SeatInv: GetSeatStatus(inventoryId)
    SeatInv-->>Purchase: held and token valid
    Purchase->>OutSys: GET current credit balance
    OutSys-->>Purchase: enough balance
    Purchase->>SeatInv: SellSeat(inventoryId, userId, holdToken)
    SeatInv-->>Purchase: sold
    Purchase->>Ticket: POST /tickets
    Ticket-->>Purchase: ticketId
    Purchase->>OutSys: PATCH deducted balance
    Purchase->>Ledger: POST purchase ledger entry
    Purchase-->>User: 201 ticket issued
